request.description:
Get all provinces in the Philippines

**Response Format:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [
    {
      "code": "METRO_MANILA",
      "name": "Metro Manila"
    },
    {
      "code": "CEBU",
      "name": "Cebu"
    }
  ]
}
```

**Use Case:** Populate province dropdown in address forms

Get all cities/municipalities in Metro Manila

**Response Format:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [
    {
      "code": "manila",
      "name": "Manila"
    },
    {
      "code": "quezon_city",
      "name": "Quezon City"
    },
    {
      "code": "makati",
      "name": "Makati"
    }
  ]
}
```

**Use Case:** Populate city dropdown after province selection

Get all barangays in Manila City

**Response Format:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [
    {
      "code": "B001",
      "name": "Barangay 1"
    },
    {
      "code": "B002",
      "name": "Barangay 2"
    }
  ]
}
```

**Expected:** 896+ barangays (Manila has many barangays)
